Comment: 0,0:01:04.80,0:01:06.70,orig,,0,0,0,,What, you drink? I didn't know.
Comment: 0,0:01:53.65,0:01:54.55,orig,,0,0,0,,I feel bad...
Comment: 0,0:01:55.05,0:01:58.52,orig,,0,0,0,,You do all these things while we sleep.
Comment: 0,0:02:14.25,0:02:15.65,orig,,0,0,0,,Hm, I don't know.
Comment: 0,0:02:46.36,0:02:47.60,orig,,0,0,0,,Really? No fair.
Comment: 0,0:03:21.73,0:03:22.49,orig,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Comment: 0,0:05:49.90,0:05:50.80,orig,,0,0,0,,Shh!
Comment: 0,0:06:00.60,0:06:01.80,orig,,0,0,0,,I see one of them!
Comment: 0,0:06:02.25,0:06:03.20,orig,,0,0,0,,Is he on his own?
Comment: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:05.17,orig,,0,0,0,,What is he armed with?
Comment: 0,0:06:05.40,0:06:06.10,orig,,0,0,0,,A sword.
Comment: 0,0:06:56.00,0:06:57.15,orig,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Comment: 0,0:08:06.65,0:08:09.90,orig,,0,0,0,,Keep pressuring him! That's it! Keep it on!
Comment: 0,0:08:13.75,0:08:14.55,orig,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Comment: 0,0:09:20.00,0:09:20.50,orig,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Comment: 0,0:10:01.60,0:10:02.10,orig,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Comment: 0,0:10:30.45,0:10:31.60,orig,,0,0,0,,All righty then.
Comment: 0,0:11:11.35,0:11:17.36,orig,,0,0,0,,Damnit!
Comment: 0,0:12:22.05,0:12:23.70,orig,,0,0,0,,Oh... I see.
Comment: 0,0:12:31.95,0:12:32.65,orig,,0,0,0,,Really?
Comment: 0,0:12:56.40,0:12:58.00,orig,,0,0,0,,Yeah? Okay, then.
Comment: 0,0:13:03.20,0:13:03.70,orig,,0,0,0,,'Kay.
Comment: 0,0:17:29.20,0:17:31.15,orig,,0,0,0,,Whatever. Mind your own business.
Comment: 0,0:17:40.40,0:17:42.90,orig,,0,0,0,,See, what did I just say? Every single little thing!
Comment: 0,0:18:29.00,0:18:32.60,orig,,0,0,0,,Wha?! Huh? W-Were you that cat?
Comment: 0,0:19:38.40,0:19:39.30,orig,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Comment: 0,0:20:41.40,0:20:43.35,orig,,0,0,0,,Not to mention, the girls are there now.
Comment: 0,0:21:09.20,0:21:10.70,orig,,0,0,0,,Listen up!
Comment: 0,0:21:27.40,0:21:30.55,orig,,0,0,0,,You see now? It means I'm crossing a moral boundary today.
Comment: 0,0:21:30.55,0:21:33.90,orig,,0,0,0,,Don't make me say the obvious, it's embarrassing.

Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.60,0:00:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Manato?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.65,0:00:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruhiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.65,0:00:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.25,0:00:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.45,0:00:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you drinking, Manato?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.20,0:01:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.15,0:01:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.80,0:01:06.70,fix,,0,0,0,,Ohhh, you drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.20,0:01:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a place near the square on\NHanazono Street called Shelly's Tavern.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.75,0:01:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's become a hangout place for Volunteer Soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.55,0:01:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I was gathering information there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.85,0:01:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.50,0:01:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you'd go out of your way to do that for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.10,0:01:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Drinks are definitely not cheap for dirt-poor people like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.50,0:01:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I've actually gotten used to living like this pretty quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.95,0:01:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.90,0:01:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.65,0:01:55.80,fix,,0,0,0,,Somehow... sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.90,0:01:58.52,fix,,0,0,0,,You do it all while we sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.80,0:02:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking of changing locations tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.20,0:02:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a place with monsters\Nthat even we should be able to beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.90,0:02:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You should've taken me with you to the tavern.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.30,0:02:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you drink, Haruhiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.25,0:02:15.70,fix,,0,0,0,,Hmmm, who knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.20,0:02:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if I've had alcohol before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.00,0:02:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.30,0:02:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, I kind of like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.70,0:02:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So maybe I actually wanted to drink, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.75,0:02:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope we can go with everybody next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.55,0:02:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.30,0:02:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.20,0:02:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How was the Thief Guild?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.30,0:02:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm, I didn't expect it to be so rough, and my teacher was crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.15,0:02:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,She was pretty, but scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.40,0:02:47.60,fix,,0,0,0,,Ehhh, nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.15,0:02:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a strict, thick-bearded master with a painfully loud voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.55,0:02:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It was so bad that my ears were hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.85,0:02:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How much did you get yelled at?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.10,0:03:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.25,0:03:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough to make me believe I was born just to be yelled at.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.15,0:03:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He was constantly yelling at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.60,0:03:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know stuff like that happens to you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.60,0:03:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It does.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.05,0:03:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.85,0:03:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Manato...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.15,0:03:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.73,0:03:22.49,fix,,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.70,0:03:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The moon... is so red.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.95,0:03:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.55,0:03:39.10,Italics,,0,0,0,,I don't know where this place is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.10,0:03:43.40,Italics,,0,0,0,,I don't know how we got here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.65,0:03:47.05,Italics,,0,0,0,,But... one thing is for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.15,0:03:51.15,Italics,,0,0,0,,The moon wasn't red at the other place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.30,0:03:55.50,Italics,,0,0,0,,A red moon is just... weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.10,0:04:06.50,op/ed,,0,0,0,,Repeating a yesterday filled with scrapes,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.50,0:04:11.30,op/ed,,0,0,0,,We clear the path to a hopeful tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.35,0:04:26.40,op/ed,,0,0,0,,I wonder what remains
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.40,0:04:29.60,op/ed,,0,0,0,,in both these tiny hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.60,0:04:35.95,op/ed,,0,0,0,,The voice I raised upwards scattered into the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.95,0:04:39.25,op/ed,,0,0,0,,The reality I've gamed is hazy,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.25,0:04:42.35,op/ed,,0,0,0,,and even if I can't see ahead of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.35,0:04:45.65,op/ed,,0,0,0,,I can keep moving forward on this long road
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.65,0:04:49.75,op/ed,,0,0,0,,if I'm with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.75,0:04:56.00,op/ed,,0,0,0,,Connecting a bond covered in dust,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.00,0:05:02.35,op/ed,,0,0,0,,We join back to back in the past and future.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.35,0:05:08.80,op/ed,,0,0,0,,Repeating an answer full of mistakes,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.80,0:05:16.80,op/ed,,0,0,0,,I will reach out my hands to seek the light, again and again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.95,0:05:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Is a gobs there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.60,0:06:02.20,fix,,0,0,0,,There is. One.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.20,0:06:03.15,fix,,0,0,0,,On his own?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.15,0:06:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.55,0:06:05.40,fix,,0,0,0,,He armed?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.40,0:06:06.20,fix,,0,0,0,,With sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.85,0:06:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.90,0:06:48.85,Italics,,0,0,0,,We should have decided on some sort of signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.25,0:06:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.95,0:06:57.15,fix_it,,0,0,0,,Stupid Ranta!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.15,0:06:59.65,Italics,,0,0,0,,There's no point in a surprise attack if you're that loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.60,0:07:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.60,0:07:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice, Yume!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.95,0:07:09.10,Italics,,0,0,0,,Who are you fighting? Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.60,0:07:18.50,Italics,,0,0,0,,What? So I'm attacking first?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.50,0:07:20.20,Italics,,0,0,0,,It's not what Thieves usually do!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.00,0:07:25.70,Italics,,0,0,0,,Our reaches are completely different.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.70,0:07:27.80,Italics,,0,0,0,,I know, I'll use a Slap to his wrist!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.70,0:07:30.60,Italics,,0,0,0,,Too shallow?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.75,0:07:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't stop moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.40,0:07:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hatred!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.80,0:07:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.80,0:07:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Marque, Em, Parc!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.10,0:07:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Moguzo, get in front of the goblin!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.00,0:07:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.05,0:08:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody, surround him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.15,0:08:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let him run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.80,0:08:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Moguzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.70,0:08:08.20,fix,,0,0,0,,Keep pressuring him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.20,0:08:09.90,fix,,0,0,0,,Pressuring! Pressuring!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.55,0:08:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I get him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.65,0:08:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I just cut into his... his bone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.15,0:08:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.45,0:08:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,H-He's scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.75,0:08:37.05,Italics,,0,0,0,,The goblin is desperate, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.80,0:08:39.00,Italics,,0,0,0,,He doesn't want to be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.00,0:08:40.20,Italics,,0,0,0,,There's no way he would.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.70,0:08:42.20,Italics,,0,0,0,,"I'll get you before you get me."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.90,0:08:44.60,Italics,,0,0,0,,Of course I don't understand his words...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.10,0:08:47.35,Italics,,0,0,0,,...but even I can tell what he's saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.75,0:08:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lose your heads, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.05,0:08:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's kill or be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.20,0:08:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm gonna kill this guy and accumulate my Vice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.95,0:09:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just as scared as we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.00,0:09:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh-Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.60,0:09:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Gobs is a pretty tough one, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.05,0:09:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Marque, Em, Parc!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.80,0:09:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I got him...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.80,0:09:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.30,0:09:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.30,0:09:59.00,Alt,,0,0,0,,Haru-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.35,0:10:02.35,Alt,,0,0,0,,Were you watching, {Lord }Skullhell-sama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.80,0:10:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Gently, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.84,0:10:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,O light, return to Lumiaris' divine protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.55,0:10:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Cure!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.75,0:10:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this... the booty?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.85,0:10:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Some animal's fang and... it's a silver coin?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.40,0:10:31.85,fix,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.85,0:10:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...to accumulate a Vice, the monster\Nmust die by the hand of a Dark Knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.90,0:10:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, a body part must be offered to the guild's altar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.40,0:10:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, an ear's kinda big.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.00,0:10:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,A claw should work, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.55,0:10:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't Moguzo deal the final blow?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.20,0:10:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! You're right! Moguzo, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.20,0:10:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This was supposed to be my special first Vice!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.60,0:10:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.50,0:10:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.85,0:11:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't want to die, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.20,0:11:14.70,fix,,0,0,0,,Damnit! Damn! Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.70,0:11:18.00,fix,,0,0,0,,Damn! Damn! Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.85,0:11:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Da—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.02,0:11:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.45,0:12:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This is worth about thirty coppers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.85,0:12:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a silver coin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.30,0:12:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's a little dirty and doesn't look like much...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.60,0:12:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't like my price, go ahead and take it elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.30,0:12:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be about the same everywhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.05,0:12:23.75,fix,,0,0,0,,I... see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.45,0:12:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a black wolf fang?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.25,0:12:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll buy it, if you'll take one silver for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.60,0:12:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What? This fang is worth that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.90,0:12:32.85,fix,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.85,0:12:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.60,0:12:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They're used as materials to make\Ncharms against evil, among other things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.80,0:12:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.45,0:12:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.35,0:12:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The sun's still high.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.65,0:12:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we call it a day and rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.40,0:12:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.60,0:12:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.75,0:12:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.35,0:12:58.10,fix,,0,0,0,,I see.  Okay, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.90,0:13:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then you're all excused for the rest of the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.30,0:13:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see you all tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.25,0:13:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Okaaay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.55,0:13:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.15,0:17:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a little more like a Dark Knight now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.05,0:17:31.15,fix,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.70,0:17:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to eating bones and all?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.55,0:17:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are a nitpicker, bugging\Nme about every single little thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.25,0:17:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Not about every single thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.40,0:17:43.00,fix,,0,0,0,,See, like I sad, every single little thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.50,0:17:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.45,0:17:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...it turned out all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.70,0:17:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I got to accumulate my first Vice, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.35,0:17:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What can you do if you accumulate a Vice?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.90,0:17:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I can summon a daemon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.40,0:18:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And what can that daemon do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.00,0:18:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It whispers and tells me if an enemy is near.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.20,0:18:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And sometimes it explodes a Daemon Joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.75,0:18:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.05,0:18:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean "that's all"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.10,0:18:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be a perfect partner for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.55,0:18:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.90,0:18:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be just right for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.35,0:18:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.85,0:18:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's kind of ironic that we say it'd be a good fit for you,\Nwhen we don't even know what the daemon is good for.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.25,0:18:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.75,0:18:30.75,fix,,0,0,0,,Wha?! Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.35,0:18:32.55,fix,,0,0,0,,I-It's you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.05,0:18:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a transformation skill like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.65,0:18:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.95,0:18:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just thinking how pretty the sun\Nlooked when it plopped onto my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.80,0:18:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.05,0:18:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I knew that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.20,0:18:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't scare me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.60,0:18:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem kind of flustered.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.40,0:18:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.75,0:18:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It really is beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.80,0:18:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The sunset.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.15,0:19:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I pass by here everyday...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.35,0:19:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe... I never had the time to notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.60,0:19:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Manato... you awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.70,0:19:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.40,0:19:39.30,fix,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.25,0:19:47.15,Italics,,0,0,0,,I felt like I had a lot of things I wanted to ask Manato.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.50,0:19:51.90,Italics,,0,0,0,,Like how we only made eighteen coppers a person today...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.00,0:19:55.25,Italics,,0,0,0,,...and if we'll be okay from here on out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.55,0:19:59.35,Italics,,0,0,0,,But... when I tried to ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.95,0:20:01.65,Italics,,0,0,0,,...the words didn't come out right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.20,0:20:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.40,0:20:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Nevermind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.75,0:20:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Okay, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.45,0:20:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.50,0:20:16.25,Italics,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess today wasn't bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.50,0:20:20.05,Italics,,0,0,0,,Nobody knows what will happen in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.90,0:20:23.10,Italics,,0,0,0,,Something even better might happen tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.35,0:20:25.25,Italics,,0,0,0,,So, it's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.85,0:20:27.00,Italics,,0,0,0,,At least, for now it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.00,0:20:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Be back in a jiff.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.45,0:20:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranta, you're awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.65,0:20:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.80,0:20:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The baths, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.60,0:20:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The baths!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.55,0:20:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.50,0:20:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You just took one!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.40,0:20:43.70,fix,,0,0,0,,Not to mention it's the girls time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.70,0:20:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What a numbskull.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.20,0:20:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You still don't get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.90,0:20:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, are you...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.80,0:20:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you're feeling better, but you\Nhave got to draw the line somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.65,0:20:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? I'm always feeling great.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.80,0:20:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Super great!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.75,0:21:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm burning so furiously that I can't hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.22,0:21:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,My passion is glistening!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.70,0:21:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are just carnal desires.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.20,0:21:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}thought{\i0} you were studying the bath walls carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.20,0:21:11.00,fix,,0,0,0,,Listen me carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.00,0:21:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,At this very moment, the girls are bare,\Nwashing their hair and bodies, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.00,0:21:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Just imagine, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.15,0:21:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one thing a man should do!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.55,0:21:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're shameless.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.15,0:21:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Call me Shameless-sama{ the Great}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.65,0:21:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The great and noble Shameless King-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.40,0:21:28.20,fix,,0,0,0,,You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.20,0:21:30.55,fix,,0,0,0,,Today we crossed a moral boundary.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.55,0:21:32.00,fix,,0,0,0,,Then it should be obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.00,0:21:34.00,fix,,0,0,0,,Don't make me say it, it's embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.00,0:21:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This and that has nothing to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.65,0:21:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are your morals?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.05,0:21:39.50,Alt,,0,0,0,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.50,0:21:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.50,0:21:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ranta!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.85,0:21:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranta-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.15,0:21:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranta, you idiot! Sicko! Lecher! Pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.20,0:21:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Get lost and never come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.20,0:22:00.35,Italics,,0,0,0,,We ended up getting caught in the mess and apologizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.15,0:22:04.50,Italics,,0,0,0,,Ranta, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.95,0:22:23.25,op/ed,,0,0,0,,When I try touching
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.35,0:22:29.50,op/ed,,0,0,0,,the dry air after a rain,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.60,0:22:36.15,op/ed,,0,0,0,,like a sprouting flower,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.15,0:22:42.45,op/ed,,0,0,0,,fragments of memories overflow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.45,0:22:55.10,op/ed,,0,0,0,,The warmth you gave this hand
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.10,0:23:03.90,op/ed,,0,0,0,,led me to a future I can treasure
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.90,0:23:06.66,op/ed,,0,0,0,,always.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.66,0:23:13.85,op/ed,,0,0,0,,I chased your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.85,0:23:19.50,op/ed,,0,0,0,,I wonder when you became so strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.50,0:23:26.45,op/ed,,0,0,0,,I will probably find what I searched the vast world for
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.45,0:23:34.00,op/ed,,0,0,0,,at the end of this journey.
